        <div class="flex-auto">
          <h5 class="h3 mt0 mb1 regular dark-blue">Scott Hurff</h5>
          <h5 class="h4 mt0 mb1 med-gray regular">
              Head of Product, 
              <a target="_blank" href="https://chill.com/">Chill</a>
          </h5>
          <p class="med-gray">I'm an entrepreneur and product designer living in Los Angeles, California. I'm on the founding team of <a href="https://chill.com/" target="_blank">Chill</a>, where I lead product. 

I'm writing a book called <a href="http://scotthurff.com/perfecting-product-design/" target="_blank">"Perfecting Product Design."</a> It's an examination of product design and a step-by-step guide that teaches product designers how to think smarter, act faster, and simplify the process of turning ideas into usable products.</p>
        </div>
